Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.02,0:01:33.98,Fiction_Disclaimer,Text,0,0,0,,{\fad(235,178)\blur1}This story is a work of fiction. The names of all of the characters, organizations, and so on\N are imaginary. It also bears no connection to any specific real-life events.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.36,0:02:17.86,sign_3246_9_Verdigris_House,Text,0,0,0,,Verdigris House
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.06,0:03:34.81,italics,Maomao,0,0,0,,That shrewd old bag, always trying\N to make me a courtesan...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.82,0:03:52.54,italics,Maomao,0,0,0,,Could it be? Kidnappers?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.67,0:04:43.88,sign_6731_39_Three_months_lat,Text,0,0,0,,{\fad(529,1)\blur1\fscx90}Three months later
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.17,0:04:48.18,Ep_Title,Episode Title,0,0,0,,{\fad(490,435)\fscx98\blur1\pos(599,304)}Episode 1: Maomao
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.11,0:05:03.18,italics,Maomao,0,0,0,,I'm not sure if I was sold off or ransomed, \Nbut annoyingly, it's already been three months.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.15,0:05:25.50,italics,Maomao,0,0,0,,The rear palace is a garden of women \Nwho are to give birth to the emperor's children.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.50,0:05:27.99,italics,Maomao,0,0,0,,No men are allowed to enter.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.74,0:05:33.22,italics,Maomao,0,0,0,,The only people allowed in here \Nare the emperor, his kin,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.54,0:05:38.85,italics,Maomao,0,0,0,,and eunuchs, "formerly male" individuals \Nwho lost an important part of their body.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.40,0:05:42.62,italics,Maomao,0,0,0,,It's a huge collective of two thousand \Nconcubines and servants,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.62,0:05:44.97,italics,Maomao,0,0,0,,and one thousand eunuchs.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.67,0:05:49.37,italics,Maomao,0,0,0,,Unlike the high, mid, \Nand low-ranking concubines,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.37,0:05:54.37,italics,Maomao,0,0,0,,we serving girls are expendable \Nand can lose our lives at any moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.05,0:05:58.96,italics,Maomao,0,0,0,,Next in line are the shut-in, \Nlow-ranking concubines.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.96,0:06:02.40,italics,Maomao,0,0,0,,I guess, at the very least, I get paid.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.07,0:06:16.85,italics,Maomao,0,0,0,,Many of the servants are illiterate.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.45,0:06:19.10,italics,Maomao,0,0,0,,In order to work in the rear palace,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.10,0:06:22.01,italics,Maomao,0,0,0,,they're taught the bare minimum \Nessentials of etiquette.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.01,0:06:24.74,italics,Maomao,0,0,0,,But reading and writing \Nis a whole different story.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.31,0:06:31.62,italics,Maomao,0,0,0,,The raise I would get for being literate \Nwould just get swiped by my kidnappers.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.53,0:06:36.67,italics,Maomao,0,0,0,,That said, even servants like us \Ncould become low-ranking concubines.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.67,0:06:37.62,italics,Maomao,0,0,0,,What's key is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.99,0:06:41.38,italics,Maomao,0,0,0,,Looks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.38,0:06:42.63,italics,Maomao,0,0,0,,Freckles.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.89,0:06:43.88,italics,Maomao,0,0,0,,Flat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.26,0:06:48.06,italics,Maomao,0,0,0,,Given my skin-and-bones look, \Nthat's not applicable to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.48,0:06:58.14,italics,Maomao,0,0,0,,If I stood out, my life would be\N at risk. I'm better off just laying low.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.44,0:07:02.46,italics,Maomao,0,0,0,,All I have to do is work hard. \NI'll be out in two years.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.65,0:11:20.51,italics,Maomao,0,0,0,,Is that flustered eunuch \Nin the middle the physician?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.51,0:11:22.24,italics,Maomao,0,0,0,,What a stupid quack.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.57,0:11:26.74,italics,Maomao,0,0,0,,He seriously still hasn't noticed? After \Nspending all that time near the concubines?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.23,0:11:27.98,italics,Maomao,0,0,0,,Or rather...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.45,0:11:30.50,italics,Maomao,0,0,0,,Maybe he really doesn't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.14,0:11:35.23,italics,Maomao,0,0,0,,Death of the infants. \NHeadache, stomachache, nausea.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.23,0:11:39.32,italics,Maomao,0,0,0,,And most of all, how \NLady Lihua seems so worn out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.32,0:11:42.76,italics,Maomao,0,0,0,,As I thought, this is no curse.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.15,0:11:45.02,italics,Maomao,0,0,0,,The only issue is, how do I tell them?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.22,0:11:48.18,italics,Maomao,0,0,0,,If only I could find something to write with...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.27,0:12:34.94,italics,Maomao,0,0,0,,Barely a month passed before word got around
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.94,0:12:37.57,italics,Maomao,0,0,0,,that the prince had passed away.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.25,0:13:29.45,italics,Jinshi,0,0,0,,Coming to think of it, back then...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.83,0:13:33.14,flashback,Maomao,0,0,0,,If only I could find something to write with...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.25,0:14:22.09,italics,Maomao,0,0,0,,Serving girls getting summoned by \Nthe high officials can't be good news...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.54,0:14:25.26,italics,Maomao,0,0,0,,Or do they just want more workers?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.98,0:14:46.74,italics,Maomao,0,0,0,,Who is this arrogant-looking woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.13,0:14:58.94,italics,Maomao,0,0,0,,That's a man?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.94,0:15:04.88,italics,Maomao,0,0,0,,Ah, that must be the good-looking \Neunuch that Xiaolan was talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.88,0:15:09.88,italics,Maomao,0,0,0,,That's a waste. He's so handsome,\Nbut he can't have children.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.89,0:15:15.89,sign_21864_187_You_with_the_fre,Text,0,0,0,,{\pos(289.6,18)}You with the freckles, stay here
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.78,0:15:15.89,italics,Maomao,0,0,0,,Huh? Freckles? Stay...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.69,0:15:17.74,italics,Maomao,0,0,0,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.02,0:15:29.07,italics,Maomao,0,0,0,,Did I do something to get attention?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.07,0:15:31.18,italics,Maomao,0,0,0,,Wait, did the message from the other day...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.28,0:15:33.11,italics,Maomao,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.11,0:15:36.30,italics,Maomao,0,0,0,,I'm the only servant here who can read!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.30,0:15:39.75,italics,Maomao,0,0,0,,He wrote that just now to single me out!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.75,0:15:41.50,italics,Maomao,0,0,0,,Oh no, I have to get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.05,0:15:56.01,italics,Maomao,0,0,0,,It was a trap...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.03,0:16:13.41,italics,Maomao,0,0,0,,I'll never admit it. Pretending to be ignorant \Nmakes everything easier in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.41,0:16:17.69,italics,Maomao,0,0,0,,Besides, how did this man \Nfind out about the messages?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.69,0:16:20.66,italics,Maomao,0,0,0,,I made absolutely sure nobody was around...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.26,0:16:26.13,italics,Maomao,0,0,0,,He's so mistrustful!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.27,0:16:29.66,italics,Maomao,0,0,0,,Rather, he must have nothing better to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.49,0:16:35.96,italics,Maomao,0,0,0,,What will I be punished for?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.96,0:16:38.26,italics,Maomao,0,0,0,,I hope I make it out of this alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.51,0:17:25.80,italics,Maomao,0,0,0,,I don't want to get beheaded for lying,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.80,0:17:28.02,italics,Maomao,0,0,0,,but I don't want to get involved, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.07,0:17:53.09,sign_25345_228_The_white_face_p,Text,0,0,0,,The white face powder is poison.\NDon't let the baby touch it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.59,0:18:01.97,italics,Maomao,0,0,0,,So, he figured out that much already...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.59,0:20:19.02,italics,Narrator,0,0,0,,There are some things Maomao cannot hold back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.02,0:20:22.06,italics,Narrator,0,0,0,,Curiosity, a thirst for knowledge...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.06,0:20:25.87,italics,Narrator,0,0,0,,And just a smidgen of a sense of justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.75,0:20:36.21,top,Xiaolan,0,0,0,,Hey, Maomao!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.21,0:20:39.39,top,Xiaolan,0,0,0,,Welcome back, Maomao! How was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.84,0:20:44.52,italics,Narrator,0,0,0,,And thus, Maomao became a\N lady-in-waiting of Concubine Gyokuyou,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.52,0:20:46.90,italics,Narrator,0,0,0,,recipient of the emperor's love.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.90,0:20:49.81,italics,Narrator,0,0,0,,Put simply, it was a big promotion.
