Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.67,0:01:38.90,Default,Luomen,0,0,0,,Maomao.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.32,0:01:40.25,Default,Maomao,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.16,0:01:44.44,Default,Luomen,0,0,0,,Could you deliver some medicine \Nto the Verdigris House?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.85,0:01:46.87,Default,Maomao,0,0,0,,Yeah, got it, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.38,0:01:52.57,Default,Luomen,0,0,0,,Be careful out there. \NKidnappings are on the rise.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.57,0:01:55.63,Default,Maomao,0,0,0,,I'll be fine. I'll stop by\N the herb plot on my way back.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.01,0:01:57.88,Default,Luomen,0,0,0,,Yes, please do.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.37,0:01:59.51,Default,Maomao,0,0,0,,I'm off!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.83,0:02:25.20,Default,Old Lady,0,0,0,,Huh, is this all you've got?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.20,0:02:27.72,Default,Customer,0,0,0,,It's my life savings! I beg you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.58,0:02:34.55,Default,Old Lady,0,0,0,,This is a non-starter.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.55,0:02:38.64,Default,Customer,0,0,0,,That must be Pairin, one of the famous \NThree Princesses of the Verdigris House!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.64,0:02:40.51,Default,Old Lady,0,0,0,,If you want to gawk, pay up!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.03,0:02:51.64,Default,Maomao,0,0,0,,Hmm, it's taking too long to heal.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.64,0:02:52.97,Default,Maomao,0,0,0,,I'll tweak the recipe some.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.97,0:02:54.73,Default,Pairin,0,0,0,,Oh, Maomao!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.21,0:02:56.80,Default,Maomao,0,0,0,,Hey, Pairin.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.80,0:02:59.03,Default,Pairin,0,0,0,,Hey, you have more wounds again!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.39,0:03:02.41,Default,Maomao,0,0,0,,It's just my usual drug experiments.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.62,0:03:05.32,Default,Pairin,0,0,0,,Are you eating well?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.32,0:03:08.06,Default,Maomao,0,0,0,,You seem to be very well nourished, as always.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.06,0:03:09.29,Default,Old Lady,0,0,0,,Maomao!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.29,0:03:14.00,Default,Old Lady,0,0,0,,You'd better not be setting off explosions \Nagain for your so-called experiments!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.34,0:03:19.09,Default,Old Lady,0,0,0,,Or, would you like to start\N a career as a courtesan?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.40,0:03:20.09,Default,Maomao,0,0,0,,Yikes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.79,0:03:22.81,Default,Maomao,0,0,0,,Granny, I left your meds here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.81,0:03:25.94,Default,Old Lady,0,0,0,,Say hi to your old man for me. Sheesh.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.94,0:03:27.79,Default,Joka,0,0,0,,Did I just hear Maomao's voice?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.79,0:03:29.42,Default,Meimei,0,0,0,,Hey, where's Maomao?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.42,0:03:31.06,Default,Pairin,0,0,0,,She took off.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.63,0:04:01.30,Default,Maomao,0,0,0,,Dad's gonna be really worried...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.90,0:04:20.84,Default,Guen,0,0,0,,The prince is born!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.84,0:04:23.07,Default,Guen,0,0,0,,Congratulations, Lady Lihua!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.98,0:04:33.54,Default,Hongniang,0,0,0,,The prince was born safely.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.54,0:04:35.67,Default,Gyokuyou,0,0,0,,I see. Wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.75,0:04:51.89,Default,Maomao,0,0,0,,I want meat skewers from a stall...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.71,0:04:55.64,Default,Maomao,0,0,0,,I wonder if Dad's eating properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.19,0:05:07.50,Default,Maomao,0,0,0,,The palace and the brothels are really similar.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.50,0:05:11.41,Default,Maomao,0,0,0,,If I had a choice, I'd have nothing to do \Nwith the rear palace, ever. But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.63,0:05:15.41,Default,Maomao,0,0,0,,Well, what can I do, now that I'm here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.94,0:05:19.84,Default,Maomao,0,0,0,,I was living a pretty good life \Nas an apothecary, and now...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.40,0:06:04.60,Default,Xiaolan,0,0,0,,Hey, Maomao...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.60,0:06:07.34,Default,Xiaolan,0,0,0,,Do you know which room this plate is for?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.34,0:06:11.43,Default,Maomao,0,0,0,,Oh. This one is Wisteria-9, so over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.81,0:06:13.43,Default,Xiaolan,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.33,0:07:06.39,Default,Maomao,0,0,0,,I need a drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.22,0:07:10.68,Default,Xiaolan,0,0,0,,Hey, did you hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.68,0:07:11.20,Default,Maomao,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.20,0:07:15.18,Default,Xiaolan,0,0,0,,I heard there's a super beautiful \Neunuch in the central area.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.18,0:07:18.50,Default,Xiaolan,0,0,0,,Everyone's been talking about him!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.50,0:07:19.98,Default,Maomao,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.98,0:07:23.28,Default,Xiaolan,0,0,0,,I'd like to get a glimpse of him, \Nif he's so handsome!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.28,0:07:24.17,Default,Xiaolan,0,0,0,,Am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.09,0:07:26.95,Default,Maomao,0,0,0,,A eunuch, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.21,0:07:57.45,Default,Gaoshun,0,0,0,,She has lost much weight.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.45,0:07:58.33,Default,Jinshi,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.91,0:08:06.34,Default,Gyokuyou,0,0,0,,Xiaoling...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.34,0:08:11.88,Default,Jinshi,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, the physician is busy \Nattending to the prince.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.87,0:08:15.09,Default,Gyokuyou,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.01,0:08:19.73,Default,Servant A,0,0,0,,They're only three months and six months old, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.73,0:08:23.40,Default,Servant B,0,0,0,,Yeah, both the prince and Princess Lingli...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.09,0:08:26.10,Default,Xiaolan,0,0,0,,Is it really a curse?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.17,0:08:28.36,Default,Maomao,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.36,0:08:30.80,Default,Xiaolan,0,0,0,,You didn't hear, Maomao?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.80,0:08:34.25,Default,Xialoan,0,0,0,,The entire rear palace \Nis buzzing about this rumor.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.66,0:08:37.85,Default,Xiaolan,0,0,0,,The deaths of all the heirs \Nborn in the rear palace!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.37,0:08:43.97,Default,Xiaolan,0,0,0,,All three of the emperor's children \Nborn so far grew weak and passed away!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.97,0:08:45.58,Default,Xiaolan,0,0,0,,Doesn't that seem weird?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.58,0:08:46.97,Default,Maomao,0,0,0,,All three?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.97,0:08:49.37,Default,Xiaolan,0,0,0,,And it looks like the same\Nthing's happening now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.37,0:08:50.75,Default,Maomao,0,0,0,,You mean they're unwell?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.75,0:08:57.89,Default,Xiaolan,0,0,0,,Yes! And this time, the doctor went to visit \Nboth Lady Gyokuyou and Lady Lihua!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.15,0:08:59.22,Default,Maomao,0,0,0,,Huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.60,0:09:02.80,Default,Xiaolan,0,0,0,,The emperor doesn't have an empress \Nconsort, so that makes Lady Lihua,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.80,0:09:05.31,Default,Xiaolan,0,0,0,,who gave birth to the prince, \Nthe empress consort, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.93,0:09:07.94,Default,Maomao,0,0,0,,Naturally, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.94,0:09:10.17,Default,Maomao,0,0,0,,Since there is no empress consort,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.17,0:09:11.98,Default,Maomao,0,0,0,,Concubine Lihua gave birth to the prince,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.98,0:09:14.56,Default,Maomao,0,0,0,,so she should be considered \Nthe top of the rear palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.56,0:09:19.47,Default,Xiaolan,0,0,0,,But then, rumor says the emperor \Nfavors Lady Gyokuyou.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.47,0:09:23.45,Default,Xiaolan,0,0,0,,They say that could be \Nrelated to the curse, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.45,0:09:26.04,Default,Maomao,0,0,0,,A power struggle...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.41,0:09:32.73,Default,Xiaolan,0,0,0,,Lady Lihua might be worse off, \Nsince the doctor is always with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.73,0:09:34.33,Default,Maomao,0,0,0,,Lady Lihua herself is sick, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.33,0:09:37.85,Default,Xiaolan,0,0,0,,Yeah, mother and child both. \NHead and stomach aches.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.85,0:09:40.30,Default,Xiaolan,0,0,0,,Nausea too, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.36,0:09:45.10,Default,Maomao,0,0,0,,Headache, stomachache, nausea...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.10,0:09:48.23,Default,Xiaolan,0,0,0,,It {\i1}has{\i0} to be a curse!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.90,0:09:52.25,Default,Maomao,0,0,0,,Curses are stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.25,0:09:53.90,Default,Xiaolan,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.05,0:10:01.10,Default,Maomao,0,0,0,,Headache, stomachache, nausea...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.10,0:10:03.70,Default,Maomao,0,0,0,,Poison is a possibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.70,0:10:05.69,Default,Maomao,0,0,0,,No, if it's over the position of imperial heir,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.69,0:10:07.90,Default,Maomao,0,0,0,,it doesn't make sense to go after the princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.90,0:10:10.97,Default,Maomao,0,0,0,,Deliberate poisoning is low on the list of possibilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.97,0:10:13.29,Default,Maomao,0,0,0,,Could an illness be more likely?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.50,0:10:16.66,Default,Maomao,0,0,0,,Perhaps something hereditary?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.49,0:10:22.22,Default,Maomao,0,0,0,,Why am I taking a rumor so seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.86,0:10:25.78,Default,Maomao,0,0,0,,It's all just conjecture.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.51,0:10:28.67,Default,Maomao,0,0,0,,But still...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.99,0:10:32.10,Default,Maomao,0,0,0,,I guess I can take a quick peek.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.59,0:10:39.94,Default,Maomao,0,0,0,,Given this is where all the high-ranked \Nconcubines' pavilions are,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.94,0:10:44.73,Default,Maomao,0,0,0,,every building is exquisite, \Nright down to the individual pillars.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.42,0:10:48.87,Default,Lihua,0,0,0,,It's your fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.87,0:10:50.33,Default,Yinghua,0,0,0,,Lady Gyokuyou!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.73,0:10:54.96,Default,Lihua,0,0,0,,You're trying to curse my son, \Nbecause your child is a daughter!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.96,0:10:58.30,Default,Gyokuyou,0,0,0,,You know that's absurd!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.30,0:11:01.09,Default,Gyokuyou,0,0,0,,My Xiaoling is sick, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.58,0:11:04.11,Default,Eunuch A,0,0,0,,Lady Lihua is furious.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.11,0:11:06.18,Default,Eunuch B,0,0,0,,I feel sorry for Lady Gyokuyou.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.46,0:11:07.43,Default,Gaoshun,0,0,0,,Master Jinshi...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.48,0:11:14.22,Default,Gyokuyou,0,0,0,,That's why I'd like you to examine \Nmy daughter's state, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.22,0:11:16.65,Default,Guen,0,0,0,,Yes... Well... Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.82,0:12:44.61,Default,Gyokuyou,0,0,0,,It seems like you have a question for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.19,0:12:46.57,Default,Jinshi,0,0,0,,Is that...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.09,0:12:52.02,Default,Gyokuyou,0,0,0,,The day I visited the Crystal Pavilion \Nto ask to have my daughter examined,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.56,0:12:56.98,Default,Gyokuyou,0,0,0,,I found this on the windowsill, \Ntied to this branch.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.06,0:12:59.85,Default,Jinshi,0,0,0,,A rhododendron.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.95,0:13:04.55,Default,Gyokuyou,0,0,0,,"The white face powder is poison. \NDon't let the baby touch it."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.63,0:13:07.68,Default,Gyokuyou,0,0,0,,It truly is a sin to be ignorant.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.29,0:13:12.75,Default,Jinshi,0,0,0,,The palace physician would not take \Nsuch a roundabout approach.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.75,0:13:17.62,Default,Gyokuyou,0,0,0,,Agreed. He never could seem \Nto figure out how to treat the prince.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.62,0:13:19.94,Default,Jinshi,0,0,0,,Who could have sent this message?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.55,0:13:22.94,Default,Gyokuyou,0,0,0,,I'd like you to find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.68,0:13:38.96,Default,Jinshi,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.37,0:13:42.30,Default,Jinshi,0,0,0,,May I keep this for the time being?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.47,0:13:51.85,Default,Xiaolan,0,0,0,,I heard the emperor is visiting \NLady Gyokuyou a lot,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.85,0:13:54.39,Default,Xiaolan,0,0,0,,to show his love for \Nthe surviving princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.78,0:13:56.59,Default,Maomao,0,0,0,,What about Lady Lihua?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.59,0:13:59.09,Default,Xiaolan,0,0,0,,Haven't heard anything about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.63,0:14:01.47,Default,Maomao,0,0,0,,How convenient.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.47,0:14:03.67,Default,Eunuch C,0,0,0,,Oh, there you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.11,0:14:07.65,Default,Eunuch C,0,0,0,,You are to report to the Matron \Nof the Serving Women immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.65,0:14:09.85,Default,Xiaolan,0,0,0,,You're being summoned?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.27,0:14:12.16,Default,Maomao,0,0,0,,For what, I wonder?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.98,0:14:16.91,Default,Eunuch C,0,0,0,,All right, all of you who've \Ngathered here, head inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.97,0:14:39.48,Default,Jinshi,0,0,0,,Thank you all for coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.27,0:14:52.29,Default,Jinshi,0,0,0,,I am Jinshi, manager of the rear palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.13,0:15:23.72,Default,Jinshi,0,0,0,,We're done here. You may\N all return to your rooms.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.72,0:15:24.53,Default,Servant 1,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.53,0:15:25.65,Default,Servant 2,0,0,0,,What was that about?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.75,0:15:45.96,Default,Jinshi,0,0,0,,Come now, I just told you to stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.57,0:15:48.34,Default,Jinshi,0,0,0,,Just keep quiet and follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.30,0:16:01.51,Default,Jinshi,0,0,0,,This is odd. I looked you up. \NIt said you couldn't read.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.20,0:16:07.40,Default,Maomao,0,0,0,,I am of lowly birth. It must be a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.87,0:16:31.74,Default,Hongniang,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.74,0:16:33.09,Default,Jinshi,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.32,0:16:44.30,Default,Jinshi,0,0,0,,I brought her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.77,0:16:45.73,Default,Gyokuyou,0,0,0,,Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.06,0:16:52.90,Default,Gyokuyou,0,0,0,,Thank you for your trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.70,0:16:58.95,Default,Maomao,0,0,0,,I'm so glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.15,0:17:01.45,Default,Gyokuyou,0,0,0,,So, it was you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.34,0:17:06.96,Default,Gyokuyou,0,0,0,,Thank you for saving Lingli's life.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.96,0:17:10.46,Default,Maomao,0,0,0,,P-Please, I'm not worthy of such kindness!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.26,0:17:14.81,Default,Gyokuyou,0,0,0,,No, I can't ever thank you enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.45,0:17:17.97,Default,Gyokuyou,0,0,0,,You are my baby's savior.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.97,0:17:20.75,Default,Maomao,0,0,0,,Perhaps you have the wrong person?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.75,0:17:23.06,Default,Maomao,0,0,0,,There must be a misunderstanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.54,0:17:35.11,Default,Jinshi,0,0,0,,Concubine Gyokuyou showed me something.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.51,0:17:41.89,Default,Jinshi,0,0,0,,Did you know this fabric is used \Nin the clothing for the serving girls?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.54,0:17:45.05,Default,Maomao,0,0,0,,It does look similar, I suppose...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.05,0:17:48.99,Default,Jinshi,0,0,0,,Yes, for those who work on clothing, I hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.99,0:17:53.09,Default,Jinshi,0,0,0,,Like a laundry worker, such as yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.09,0:17:56.84,Default,Jinshi,0,0,0,,Did you rip apart a skirt, perhaps?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.43,0:18:07.27,Default,Jinshi,0,0,0,,Now, you will explain why you put \Nthat flower on the windowsill.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.03,0:18:21.60,Default,Maomao,0,0,0,,Because I figured out what was wrong that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.60,0:18:23.33,Default,Maomao,0,0,0,,That the cause was the makeup powder.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.71,0:18:26.96,Default,Maomao,0,0,0,,There were many courtesans
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.96,0:18:30.33,Default,Maomao,0,0,0,,who used high-end powder \Nin the brothels that I grew up in.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.91,0:18:37.63,Default,Maomao,0,0,0,,Most of them were poisoned \Nby it and lost their lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.79,0:18:44.97,Default,Maomao,0,0,0,,They tried to trade life \Nfor beauty and lost both.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.45,0:18:59.07,Default,Maomao,0,0,0,,I used to be an apothecary, \Nso I know a few things about poisons.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.20,0:19:09.04,Default,Jinshi,0,0,0,,That face powder...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.04,0:19:12.04,Default,Gyokuyou,0,0,0,,It was used by the baby's nurse.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.04,0:19:16.67,Default,Gyokuyou,0,0,0,,She said it has a better whitening effect \Ncompared to other powders.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.01,0:19:22.80,Default,Gyokuyou,0,0,0,,She seemed to have gotten ill too, so I gave \Nher a break. I paid her properly, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.67,0:19:24.86,Default,Jinshi,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.72,0:19:27.51,Default,Gyokuyou,0,0,0,,It truly is a sin to be ignorant.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.97,0:19:32.10,Default,Gyokuyou,0,0,0,,I should have paid more attention to\N the things that go into my baby's mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.65,0:19:34.41,Default,Jinshi,0,0,0,,I am guilty, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.41,0:19:39.19,Default,Jinshi,0,0,0,,Had I noticed sooner, I might\N have been able to save more lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.66,0:19:40.74,Default,Jinshi,0,0,0,,The Prince, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.35,0:19:47.67,Default,Gyokuyou,0,0,0,,When I saw the message, I told \NConcubine Lihua about it, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.03,0:19:55.00,Default,Gyokuyou,0,0,0,,But it seemed like everything \NI said only made her believe me less.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.45,0:19:57.78,Default,Maomao,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.30,0:20:02.76,Default,Maomao,0,0,0,,What can I do for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.56,0:20:12.94,Default,Gyokuyou,0,0,0,,Well, starting today, you'll \Nbe my lady-in-waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.15,0:20:15.21,Default,Maomao,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.27,0:20:34.26,Default,Mao,0,0,0,,No, no, no, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.26,0:20:37.63,Default,Maomao,0,0,0,,No, if I keep a low profile, \Nit shouldn't matter where I—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.98,0:20:59.57,Default,Soldier A,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.48,0:21:02.84,Default,Soldier A,0,0,0,,It's poison!
